data.name: grdOCS0115.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.HANGMOG_CODE , A.INPUT_GWA , A.INPUT_PART , DECODE(A.INPUT_PART, '*', '全体', FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME ( A.INPUT_PART, SYSDATE )) GWA_NAME , A.JUNDAL_TABLE_OUT , A.JUNDAL_PART_OUT , A.MOVE_PART , A.JUNDAL_TABLE_INP , A.JUNDAL_PART_INP , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME ( A.JUNDAL_PART_OUT, SYSDATE) GWA_NAME_OUT , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME ( A.JUNDAL_PART_INP, SYSDATE) GWA_NAME_INP , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME ( A.MOVE_PART, SYSDATE) MOVE_PART_NAME , A.START_DATE , A.END_DATE , A.HOSP_CODE , A.HANGMOG_START_DATE -- ADD SHIMO FROM OCS0115 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HANGMOG_CODE = :f_aHangmogCode AND A.HANGMOG_START_DATE = TO_DATE(:f_aHangmogStartDate,'YYYY/MM/DD') -- ADD SHIMO ORDER BY A.HANGMOG_CODE

data.name: grdOCS0103.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.SYS_DATE , A.SYS_ID , A.UPD_DATE , A.HANGMOG_CODE , A.HANGMOG_NAME , A.SLIP_CODE , A.GROUP_YN , A.POSITION , A.SEQ , A.ORDER_GUBUN , A.INPUT_CONTROL , A.JUNDAL_TABLE_OUT , A.JUNDAL_TABLE_INP , A.JUNDAL_PART_OUT , A.JUNDAL_PART_INP , A.MOVE_PART , A.DV_TIME , A.ORD_DANUI , A.DEFAULT_BOGYONG_CODE , A.SUGA_YN , A.SG_CODE , A.JAERYO_YN , A.JAERYO_CODE , A.HANGMOG_NAME_INX , A.DISPLAY_YN , A.START_DATE , A.END_DATE , A.SPECIMEN_YN , A.SPECIMEN_DEFAULT , A.DEFAULT_PORTABLE_YN , A.SPECIFIC_COMMENT , A.RESER_YN_OUT , A.RESER_YN_INP , A.EMERGENCY , A.LIMIT_SURYANG , A.BOM_YN , A.RETURN_YN , A.SUBUL_CONVERT_GUBUN , A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN , A.DEFAULT_WONNAE_SAYU , A.ANTI_CANCER_YN , A.CHISIK_YN , A.NDAY_YN , A.MUHYO_YN , A.INV_JUNDAL_YN , A.POWDER_YN , A.REMARK , A.DEFAULT_DV , A.DEFAULT_SURYANG , A.NURSE_INPUT_YN , A.SUPPLY_INPUT_YN , A.LIMIT_NALSU , A.DEFAULT_WONYOI_YN , A.PORTABLE_CHECK , A.PAT_STATUS_GR , A.UPD_ID , A.HOSP_CODE , A.DEFAULT_JUSA , B.SLIP_NAME , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.JUNDAL_PART_OUT, SYSDATE) JUNDAL_PART_OUT_NAME , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.JUNDAL_PART_INP, SYSDATE) JUNDAL_PART_INP_NAME , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.MOVE_PART, SYSDATE) MOVE_PART_NAME , E.JAERYO_NAME , FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME ( 'ORD_DANUI', E.SUBUL_DANUI) SUBUL_DANUI_NAME , TO_CHAR(E.BULYONG_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') JEARYO_BULYONG_DATE , CASE WHEN A.ORDER_GUBUN IN ('C', 'D') THEN FN_DRG_LOAD_BOGYONG_NAME ( A.DEFAULT_BOGYONG_CODE ) WHEN A.ORDER_GUBUN IN ('B') THEN FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME ('JUSA', A.DEFAULT_BOGYONG_CODE ) ELSE NULL END DEFAULT_BOGYONG_NAME , A.IF_INPUT_CONTROL , D.HUBAL_DRG_YN , D.SG_NAME , FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME ( 'ORD_DANUI', D.DANUI) SG_DANUI_NAME , TO_CHAR(D.BULYONG_YMD, 'YYYY/MM/DD') , A.RESULT_GUBUN , A.WONNAE_DRG_YN , A.YAK_KIJUN_CODE , A.YJ_CODE , G.IF_CODE , A.DEFAULT_PORTABLE_YN FROM CNV0006 F , INV0110 E ,(SELECT X.SG_CODE , X.SG_UNION , X.SG_NAME , X.BULYONG_YMD , X.DANUI , X.HUBAL_DRG_YN , X.HOSP_CODE FROM BAS0310 X WHERE X.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND X.SG_YMD = ( SELECT MAX(Z.SG_YMD) FROM BAS0310 Z WHERE Z.HOSP_CODE = X.HOSP_CODE AND Z.SG_CODE = X.SG_CODE AND Z.SG_YMD <= TRUNC(SYSDATE) ) ) D , OCS0101 C , OCS0102 B , OCS0103 A , ( SELECT A.IF_CODE , A.OCS_CODE , A.HOSP_CODE FROM IFS0003 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.MAP_GUBUN IN ( 'IF_SKR_HANGMOG_JAE', 'IF_SKR_HANGMOG', 'IF_SKR_HANGMOG_DRG') AND A.MAP_GUBUN_YMD = ( SELECT MAX(Z.MAP_GUBUN_YMD) FROM IFS0003 Z WHERE Z.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND Z.MAP_GUBUN = A.MAP_GUBUN AND Z.OCS_CODE = A.OCS_CODE AND ( Z.MAP_GUBUN_YMD < TO_DATE('9998/12/31', 'YYYY/MM/DD') OR Z.MAP_GUBUN_YMD = TO_DATE(SYSDATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') ) AND Z.IF_CODE = A.IF_CODE ) ) G WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.SLIP_CODE LIKE :f_aSlipCode AND A.HANGMOG_NAME_INX LIKE :f_aHangmogINX AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.SLIP_CODE = A.SLIP_CODE AND C.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND C.SLIP_GUBUN = B.SLIP_GUBUN AND C.SLIP_GUBUN LIKE :f_aSlipGubun AND D.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND D.SG_CODE(+) = A.SG_CODE AND E.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND E.JAERYO_CODE(+) = A.JAERYO_CODE AND F.SG_CODE(+) = D.SG_CODE AND ( ( :f_used_yn = '%' ) OR ( :f_used_yn = '1' AND F.SG_CODE IS NOT NULL ) OR ( :f_used_yn = '2' AND F.SG_CODE IS NULL ) ) AND ( ( :f_wonnae_yn = '%' ) OR ( :f_wonnae_yn = '1' AND NVL(A.WONNAE_DRG_YN, 'N') = 'Y' ) OR ( :f_wonnae_yn = '2' AND NVL(A.WONNAE_DRG_YN, 'N') != 'Y' ) ) -- AND G.HOSP_CODE (+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND G.OCS_CODE (+) = A.HANGMOG_CODE ORDER BY A.HANGMOG_CODE
